last_episode_to_air.overview: Tragedy brings the gang back together, but it's a short-lived reunion — will Alexis make amends to secure the pieces he needs to complete his dream?

name: Nothing to See Here
overview: When an aspiring blind comedian goes after his dreams, it's him and his best friend with cerebral palsy against the world, no matter what runs them over.

episodes.name: Little Egg Eyes
episodes.overview: A night at the comedy club prompts Alexis and Charly to leave their hometown. But a new city means new challenges.

episodes.name: You’re an Inspiration
episodes.overview: After their first attempt at working fails, Alexis and Charly devise a new strategy to make ends meet. A surprise guest enters the picture.

episodes.name: You Can’t
episodes.overview: Alexis regains consciousness at a veterinary clinic — and he's instantly smitten. Charly comes up with a grand gesture to sway Alexis into staying.

episodes.name: I Just Want to Be Normal
episodes.overview: Chocho steals Alexis and Charly's business idea. The gang goes to see a performance and, as the night unfolds, punches fly — but so do sparks.

episodes.name: You Got a Stage Name?
episodes.overview: As Alexis and Charly find themselves broke once again, Alexis succumbs to doing something he hates in hopes of eventually doing what he loves.

episodes.name: A Blind Person’s Gotta Do What a Blind Person’s Gotta Do
episodes.overview: Alexis's parents express their concerns. Chocho is asked to postpone the contest. A visit to Civil Protection provides interesting insights.

episodes.name: The Dog That Caught the Car
episodes.overview: Alexis is overwhelmed by fear and nerves as his big chance looms ahead. Once again, obstacles obstruct his path — with himself being one of them.

episodes.name: Missing Piece
episodes.overview: Tragedy brings the gang back together, but it's a short-lived reunion — will Alexis make amends to secure the pieces he needs to complete his dream?
